    "description": {
      "value": "<em>Your punch has the chance to trip or move your target.</em><br/><br/><b>Prerequisites</b><br/>Improved Reposition, Improved Trip, Improved Unarmed Strike, Pummeling Style; base attack bonus +9, brawler level 5th, or monk level 5th.<br/><br/><b>Benefits</b><br/>When you use Pummeling Style to make an entire full attack or flurry of blows against a single target, if you hit with any of your attacks, you can attempt a reposition or trip combat maneuver check as a free action.<br/><br/><b>Combat Trick</b><br/>When you hit with a Pummeling Style attack, you can spend 2 stamina points to make a bull rush attempt as a free action instead of a reposition attempt.",
